Package: concept
Title: Measure Concept Change in Categorization Tasks
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Rebecca", "Albrecht",
        email = "rebecca.albrecht@cognition.uni-freiburg.de",
        role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Mikhail S.", "Spektor", role = "ctb")
    )
Description: Estimates adaptive concept change in categorization tasks using
    boundary-anchored regions of interest. The package provides
    grouping-level effect estimates, beta-binomial bootstrap intervals,
    and group-level plotting utilities.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://github.com/rebecca-albrecht/concept
